  "time_ut": 1656557090,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d8b\u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dbb \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd - \u0db6\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0da7\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Maximum Retail Price - Weight Marking is mandatory",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Consumer Affairs Authority (CAA) has issued an Extraordinary Gazette Notification making it mandatory for consumers to note the maximum retail price and weight of the package containing the final unit of all merchandise purchased at the retail price.",
        "All importers, manufacturers, manufacturers, stockists, distributors, packagers, online marketers and dealers shall clearly display on the package, wrapper or container containing the last unit of all merchandise purchased by the consumer at retail price the maximum retail price, weight or volume, date of manufacture and If packed Date of packing, Expiry date/Best before date/Active period, Batch number/Code number, Manufacturer's name, address and telephone number, Country of import if imported, Name of importer/market issuer, address , the phone number/website should be printed or recorded as an indelible label, the special gazette notification said."
      ],
